Jun 22, 2017:

"What does the rise of cooperatively owned digital platforms mean for entrepreneurs? 

What great business failures could have flourished with a different business model? 

What other possibilities are there to make a living doing the work you choose?

International expert in platform cooperatives, Trebor Scholz, will step you through how platform cooperativism challenges the ‘winner takes all’ culture exemplified by Silicon Valley. 

Trebor's talk is brought to you by Green Industries SA and New Venture Institute and was filmed when he visited us in May of 2017."


